    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tim_wise_675640",
        "quote": "Jesus was not born in a manger in central Pennsylvania. He was a man of color. And the fact that we have represented him for centuries literally as a white man speaks to the entire history of white supremacy.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tim Wise",
            "url": "/quotes/tim_wise_675640"
